,A deep pan base is a type of pizza base. It is different from a thin and crispy base.,2,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#Capricciosa,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Capricciosa is a type of pizza that includes various toppings. Specifically, it has toppings such as peperonata, olives, capers, mozzarella, anchovies, ham, and tomatoes. The combination of these toppings includes a union of tomato topping, ham topping, mozzarella topping, anchovies topping, olive topping, peperonata topping, and caper topping. Additionally, Capricciosa is distinct from other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Sloppy Giuseppe, Veneziana, American Hot, unclosed pizza, Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",31,True
,Chicken topping is a type of meat topping that typically has some mild spiciness. It is different from pepperoni sausage topping, hot spiced beef topping, and ham topping.",5,True
,Meat topping is a type of pizza topping. It is different from cheese topping, fruit topping, herb spice topping, fish topping, nut topping, sauce topping, and vegetable topping.",8,True

,Anchovies topping is a type of fish topping. It is different from mixed seafood topping and also distinct from prawns topping.,3,True
pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#Cajun,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Cajun is a type of named pizza that exclusively features a combination of mozzarella topping, onion topping, peperonata topping, prawns topping, Tobasco pepper sauce, and tomato topping. Cajun pizza must include at least some Tobasco pepper sauce, onion topping, tomato topping, mozzarella topping, peperonata topping, and prawns topping. It is distinct from other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Veneziana, American Hot, Sloppy Giuseppe, Unclosed Pizza, Mushroom, Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",30,True

,Parmense is a type of named pizza that exclusively includes a combination of tomato topping, asparagus topping, mozzarella topping, parmesan topping, and ham topping. Additionally, Parmense must have at least some mozzarella topping, some tomato topping, some parmesan topping, some asparagus topping, and some ham topping. Parmense is distinct from several other pizzas, including La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, Unclosed Pizza, Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",29,True

,Frutti di mare is a type of pizza that exclusively includes toppings such as garlic, mixed seafood, and tomato. It must have at least some tomato, mixed seafood, and garlic toppings. Frutti di mare is distinct from other pizzas like la reine, fiorentina, margherita, sloppy giuseppe, veneziana, american hot, unclosed pizza, mushroom, pollo ad astra, caprina, cajun, giardiniera, american, prince carlo, capricciosa, siciliana, parmense, rosa, soho, quattro formaggi, four seasons, and napoletana.",27,True
,Spiciness is a type of value partition. It is equivalent to something that is a union of hot, medium, and mild.",2,True
,Fruit topping is a type of pizza topping. It is distinct from cheese topping, herb spice topping, meat topping, fish topping, sauce topping, nut topping, and vegetable topping.",8,True

,Leek topping is a type of vegetable topping that has a mild spiciness. It is distinct from various other toppings, including pepper topping, petit pois topping, spinach topping, caper topping, garlic topping, mushroom topping, tomato topping, rocket topping, onion topping, olive topping, asparagus topping, and artichoke topping.",14,True

,Jalapeno pepper topping is a type of pepper topping. It is characterized by having at least some level of spiciness and heat. This topping is distinct from peperonata topping, green pepper topping, and sweet pepper topping.",5,True

,Artichoke topping is a type of vegetable topping that has at least some mild spiciness. It is distinct from various other toppings, including pepper topping, petit pois topping, leek topping, spinach topping, caper topping, garlic topping, mushroom topping, tomato topping, asparagus topping, onion topping, olive topping, and rocket topping.",14,True

pizza,http://www.co-ode.org/ontologies/pizza/2005/10/18/pizza.owl#FourSeasons,@prefix owl: <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#> .

,Four Seasons is a type of named pizza that includes various toppings. It features tomato, anchovies, mushrooms, pepperoni sausage, mozzarella, capers, and olives as its toppings. In fact, Four Seasons only includes toppings that are a combination of anchovies, capers, mozzarella, mushrooms, olives, pepperoni sausage, and tomatoes.

Additionally, Four Seasons is distinct from several other pizzas, including La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, unclosed pizza, Mushroom, Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, and Napoletana.",31,True

,The Napoletana is a type of pizza that includes several specific toppings. It features anchovies, capers, mozzarella, olives, and tomatoes. This pizza is distinct from numerous others, including La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Sloppy Giuseppe, Veneziana, and unclosed pizza. Additionally, it differs from Mushroom, Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, and Four Seasons pizzas.",29,True
,Sauce topping is a type of pizza topping. It is different from fruit topping, cheese topping, herb spice topping, meat topping, fish topping, nut topping, and vegetable topping.",8,True

,Margherita is a type of pizza. It is characterized by having toppings that include mozzarella and tomato. Specifically, a Margherita pizza has only mozzarella and tomato toppings. Margherita is distinct from other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Sloppy Giuseppe, American Hot, Veneziana, and unclosed pizza. Additionally, it is different from pizzas like Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, American, Giardiniera, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",26,True

,The Veneziana is a type of named pizza that includes a variety of toppings. Specifically, it features tomato topping, caper topping, pine kernels, mozzarella topping, onion topping, sultana topping, and olive topping. The combination of these toppings is unique to the Veneziana, which only includes the union of caper topping, mozzarella topping, olive topping, onion topping, pine kernels, sultana topping, and tomato topping.

Additionally, the Veneziana is distinct from several other pizzas, including La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, Sloppy Giuseppe, American Hot, unclosed pizza, Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Caprina, Cajun, Giardiniera, American, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",31,True

,Cajun spice topping is a type of herb spice topping. It is also a type of something that at least has some level of spiciness or heat. Additionally, Cajun spice topping is different from rosemary topping.",3,True
,Pizza is a type of domain concept and is characterized by having at least some pizza base. It is different from ice cream, pizza base, and pizza topping.",5,True

,Prince Carlo is a type of named pizza that includes various toppings. It features rosemary, mozzarella, tomato, parmesan, and leek toppings. Prince Carlo is unique in that it exclusively contains a combination of leek, mozzarella, parmesan, rosemary, and tomato toppings. Additionally, Prince Carlo is distinct from other pizzas such as La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Veneziana, Sloppy Giuseppe, Mushroom, Caprina, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, American, Giardiniera, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",29,True
,Peperoni sausage topping is a type of meat topping that typically has a medium level of spiciness. It is distinct from chicken topping, hot spiced beef topping, and ham topping.",5,True
,Peperonata topping is a type of pepper topping that has at least a medium level of spiciness. It is distinct from jalapeno pepper topping, sweet pepper topping, and green pepper topping.",5,True

,Caprina is a type of named pizza. It is a type of pizza that has at least some tomato topping, some mozzarella topping, some sundried tomato topping, and some cobertura de queijo de cabra as toppings. Caprina only includes these specific toppings: cobertura de queijo de cabra, mozzarella, sundried tomato, and tomato. Caprina is distinct from several other pizzas, including La Reine, Frutti di Mare, Fiorentina, Margherita, American Hot, Sloppy Giuseppe, Veneziana, unclosed pizza, Mushroom, Pollo ad Astra, Cajun, American, Giardiniera, Prince Carlo, Capricciosa, Siciliana, Parmense, Rosa, Soho, Quattro Formaggi, Four Seasons, and Napoletana.",28,True

It specifically has a combination of these toppings: anchovies, artichoke, garlic, ham, mozzarella, olives, and tomato.
